---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'
import { Comment } from '@/components/advanced'
import { DeferredImage } from '@/components/basic'
import { Icon, Label } from '@/components/user'

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: 'profile', text: 'Profile' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'education', text: 'Education' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'research', text: 'Research' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'donation', text: 'Donation' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'copyright', text: 'Copyright' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'theme', text: 'Theme' }
]
---

<PageLayout title='About' {headings} info='/about'>
  <h2 id='profile'>Profile<a class='anchor' href='#profile'>#</a></h2>
  <section class='not-prose mb-8 mt-5 rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4 sm:p-5'>
    <div class='grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_220px] lg:items-start'>
      <div class='flex h-full flex-col'>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center'>
          <DeferredImage
            src='/avatar/avatar.jpg'
            alt='Profile avatar'
            class='h-24 w-24 rounded-lg border p-1 object-cover'
            loading='eager'
            fetchpriority='high'
            defer={false}
            />
          <div class='flex-1'>
            <p class='m-0 text-lg font-semibold text-foreground'>KIOSHIROI / 余秋白</p>
            <p class='mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>AI Student @ BNU Zhuhai</p>
            <div class='mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2'>
              <Label title='China'>
                <Icon name='location' class='size-4' slot='icon' />
              </Label>
              <Label
                title='Github'
                as='a'
                href='https://github.com/KIOSHIROI'
                target='_blank'
                rel='noopener noreferrer'
              >
                <Icon name='github' class='size-4' slot='icon' />
              </Label>
              <Label title='Email' as='a' href='mailto:202211079360@mail.bnu.edu.cn'>
                <Icon name='email' class='size-4' slot='icon' />
              </Label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class='mt-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
          一名在不断调整方向的学生。喜欢学习底层技术，关注 AI Infra、CUDA 编程等方向。
        </p>
        <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
          希望记录自己的学习历程，分享踩过的坑和总结的经验。站在巨人的肩膀上看问题，做实验。
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class='rounded-lg bg-card p-3'>
        <p class='m-0 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-muted-foreground'>Motto</p>
        <p class='mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-foreground'>站在巨人的肩膀上看问题，做实验</p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2 id='education'>Education<a class='anchor' href='#education'>#</a></h2>
  <section class='not-prose mb-8 mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4'>
    <article class='rounded-xl border border-border bg-card transition-shadow hover:shadow-md'>
      <a
        href='https://hias.ucas.ac.cn/'
        target='_blank'
        rel='noopener noreferrer'
        class='block rounded-xl p-4 no-underline sm:p-5'
        aria-label='Open HIAS official website'
      >
        <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
          <div class='size-20 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-transparent flex items-center justify-center'>
            <img src='/images/education/ucas-badge.jpg' alt='HIAS' class='size-20 rounded object-contain' loading='lazy' />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class='mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground'>Postgraduate (推免)</div>
            <h3 class='m-0 text-base font-semibold text-foreground'>国科大杭州高等研究院</h3>
            <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>人工智能，专硕</p>
            <p class='mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>Period: 2026 - Present</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </article>
    <article class='rounded-xl border border-border bg-card transition-shadow hover:shadow-md'>
      <a
        href='https://www.bnuzh.edu.cn/'
        target='_blank'
        rel='noopener noreferrer'
        class='block rounded-xl p-4 no-underline sm:p-5'
        aria-label='Open BNU Zhuhai official website'
      >
        <div class='flex items-start gap-3'>
          <div class='size-20 shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-md bg-transparent flex items-center justify-center'>
            <img src='/images/education/bnu-badge.jpg' alt='BNU' class='size-20 rounded object-contain' loading='lazy' />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class='mb-1 text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground'>Undergraduate</div>
            <h3 class='m-0 text-base font-semibold text-foreground'>北京师范大学（珠海）</h3>
            <p class='mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>人工智能，本科</p>
            <p class='mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground'>Period: 2022 - 2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </article>
  </section>

  <h2 id='research'>Research<a class='anchor' href='#research'>#</a></h2>
  <div class='not-prose mt-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3'>
    {
      [
        {
          title: 'AI Infra',
          description: '深度学习系统、分布式训练、LLM 推理优化',
          icon: 'pytorch'
        },
        {
          title: 'CUDA',
          description: 'GPU 编程、算子优化、并行计算',
          icon: 'nvidia'
        },
        {
          title: 'Distributed Systems',
          description: '分布式存储、消息队列、RPC 框架',
          icon: 'kubernetes'
        }
      ].map((interest) => (
        <div class='group relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-4 transition-all hover:border-foreground/25 hover:shadow-md'>
          <div class='flex items-start gap-4'>
            <div class='flex size-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10 transition-colors group-hover:bg-primary/20'>
              <span class='text-xl'>{interest.icon === 'pytorch' ? '🔥' : interest.icon === 'nvidia' ? '⚡' : '☁️'}</span>
            </div>
            <div class='flex-1'>
              <p class='text-xl font-medium leading-tight text-foreground transition-colors group-hover:text-primary'>
                {interest.title}
              </p>
              <p class='text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground'>{interest.description}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))
    }
  </div>

  <h2 id='donation'>Donation<a class='anchor' href='#donation'>#</a></h2>
  <p>
    如果我的博客内容对你有所帮助，欢迎请我喝杯咖啡 ☕
  </p>
  <section class='not-prose mb-8 mt-5 flex justify-center'>
    <div class='rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-6 text-center'>
      <DeferredImage
        src='/images/award_code.jpg'
        alt='Donation QR Code'
        class='mx-auto h-64 w-64 rounded-lg object-cover'
        />
      <p class='mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>微信赞赏码</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2 id='copyright'>Copyright<a class='anchor' href='#copyright'>#</a></h2>
  <p>
    如你所见，本站中的所有原创内容及设计整体，除非特别说明，均使用 <a
      href='https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/'>CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a
    > 协议进行授权。这意味着您可以在协议允许的范围内自由地分享、复制本作品的内容及基于本作品内容进行创作，但必须注明原作者和链接，并且不得用于任何商业目的。
  </p>
  <p>
    本站中的绝大多数博客封面均选自 Pixiv 的公开作品，并已注明原作链接（Hero
    Image）。包括封面在内，本站中使用了一些来自互联网的图片等素材或商标、标志及相关知识产权，无论是否标注有
    &copy; 或 &trade;
    及其他标识，均归属它们各自的权利持有人所有，并无意侵犯其作品、商标或版权。如果本站中存在侵犯您权益的内容，请您联系我，我将尽快予以删除。
  </p>
  <img src='/icons/cc-by-nc-sa.svg' alt='CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license badge' width='160' height='56' loading='lazy' decoding='async' />

  <h2 id='theme'>Theme<a class='anchor' href='#theme'>#</a></h2>
  <p>
    本博客基于 Astro 搭建，主题基于 <a href='https://github.com/Axi404/Axi-Blog'>Astro-Axi</a>。
    该主题在 Astro 的 <a href='https://astro-pure.js.org/docs'>Pure</a>, <a
      href='https://github.com/chrismwilliams/astro-theme-cactus'>Cactus</a
    > 以及 <a href='https://astro-theme-resume.vercel.app/'>Resume</a> 主题的基础之上进行了大量修改。
  </p>

  <Comment slot='bottom' />
</PageLayout>
